metadata.name: Luv-chan SWEET HEAVEN Splash
metadata.description:
This work is the fan art of Luv-chan who is  an original character of Luv. 
Luv is one of a creator whom I respect.
Please imagine if you fall in love someone, you will be drive to think that person.
When I saw Luv-chan character, I feel to fabulous emotion.
In this reason,I needed to draw ‘Luv-chan’ as a creator.
Because she is charming and tempting so much.
I imagined that Luv-chan was surrounded with lots of sweets, and was having fun.
This image brought to me a heavenly feeling.
I appreciated this experience drawing this work.
If I can share this sensation with someone, I’m very happy.
Thank you for finding this work, everyone.
Thank you for giving opportunity to draw, Luv-chan.
I wish you all the best!

Respected creator : Luv 
Twitter: @luvluv_eth
Foundation: @luvluvvox
Size:6071×8598 dpi png
